### RULES ###

### tuple ### allow tcp 47000:49000 ::/0 any ::/0 in
-A ufw6-user-input -p tcp -m multiport --dports 47000:49000 -j ACCEPT

### tuple ### allow tcp 47000:49000 ::/0 any ::/0 out
-A ufw6-user-output -p tcp -m multiport --dports 47000:49000 -j ACCEPT

### tuple ### allow udp 47000:49000 ::/0 any ::/0 in
